episodes.title: The Vampire Witch Sex Cult l Tinder Date Gone Wrong
episodes.description: A vampire, a witch, and a Tinder date gone horribly wrong. In this video, we dive into the disturbing case of Aubrey Trail and Bailey Boswell—a self-proclaimed vampire and his "queen witch"—who lured 24-year-old Sydney Loofe into a twisted world of manipulation, sex, and murder. What started as a casual Tinder date ended in a gruesome killing that shocked the nation. This is the true story behind the so-called Vampire Witch Sex Cult.
